text: "More to Life" is a 1991 song by Cliff Richard and is the theme song to the BBC tv series Trainer. It went to number 23 in the United Kingdom. ==Track listing== UK 7" single (EM 205), CD single (CDEM 205), cassette (TCEM 205) #"More to Life" #"Mo's Theme" (instrumental) ==References== Category:1991 songs Category:Cliff Richard songs
